flowchart TD
    A[Policy Change Request] --> B[Impact Assessment]
    B --> C{Change Scope}
    C -->|Rate Changes| D[Rate Table Updates]
    C -->|Rule Modifications| E[Business Rule Changes]
    C -->|Eligibility Changes| F[Semantic Ontology Updates]
    
    D --> D1[Access Rate Management System]
    D1 --> D2[Update Rate Tables]
    D2 --> D3[Validate Rate Calculations]
    D3 --> D4{Validation Passed?}
    D4 -->|No| D5[Correct Rate Errors]
    D4 -->|Yes| D6[Schedule Rate Deployment]
    D5 --> D2
    
    E --> E1[Access Rule Repository]
    E1 --> E2[Modify Drools Rules]
    E2 --> E3[Test Rule Logic]
    E3 --> E4{Test Results}
    E4 -->|Failed| E5[Debug and Fix Rules]
    E4 -->|Passed| E6[Request Rule Review]
    E5 --> E2
    
    F --> F1[Access Ontology Framework]
    F1 --> F2[Update OWL Definitions]
    F2 --> F3[Validate Semantic Consistency]
    F3 --> F4{Consistency Check}
    F4 -->|Failed| F5[Resolve Ontology Conflicts]
    F4 -->|Passed| F6[Test Semantic Translation]
    F5 --> F2
    
    D6 --> G[Policy Approval Workflow]
    E6 --> G
    F6 --> G
    
    G --> H[Senior Policy Review]
    H --> I{Approval Status}
    I -->|Approved| J[Schedule Implementation]
    I -->|Rejected| K[Return for Revision]
    I -->|Approved with Conditions| L[Implement Conditions]
    
    K --> M[Revise Policy Changes]
    M --> B
    
    L --> N[Apply Required Modifications]
    N --> J
    
    J --> O[Create Deployment Plan]
    O --> P[Notify Stakeholders]
    P --> Q[Prepare Test Environment]
    Q --> R[Execute Pre-deployment Testing]
    R --> S{Testing Successful?}
    S -->|No| T[Investigate Test Failures]
    S -->|Yes| U[Deploy to Staging]
    
    T --> V[Fix Identified Issues]
    V --> R
    
    U --> W[Staging Environment Testing]
    W --> X{Staging Tests Pass?}
    X -->|No| Y[Rollback Staging Changes]
    X -->|Yes| Z[Production Deployment]
    
    Y --> AA[Analyze Staging Failures]
    AA --> V
    
    Z --> BB[Monitor Production Impact]
    BB --> CC{Deployment Successful?}
    CC -->|Yes| DD[Complete Deployment]
    CC -->|No| EE[Emergency Rollback]
    
    EE --> FF[Incident Response]
    FF --> GG[Root Cause Analysis]
    GG --> V
    
    DD --> HH[Update Documentation]
    HH --> II[Training Material Updates]
    II --> JJ[Communication to Operations]
    JJ --> KK[Deployment Complete]
